 been physically sat next to her, you just know it.

12
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:33,960
 So, you know, I really feel that the word

13
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:37,440
 that she has for us today is a prophetic word for us,

14
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:39,720
 especially for us at The Vine.

15
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:42,240
 You know, we've been going through a season of Uncharted,

16
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:44,600
 we've been going through this time of, you know,

17
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:46,880
 pushing through with the Ezra series,

18
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,360
 the worship and the weeping,

19
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:53,360
 and just seeing God in the midst of the rubble, right?

20
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:57,240
 And seeing God even in the unknown

21
