 - Father, I thank you for Danielle.

37
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:46,400
 I thank you that she has given a lot this weekend,

38
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:50,480
 but it is from a well of wisdom, of experience,

39
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,020
 but also love for you.

40
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:56,840
 I thank you, Father, that she loves your word.

41
00:01:56,840 --> 00:02:00,080
 There's a depth that she has knowledge about.

42
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:05,080
 Her curiosity to imagine you is just,

43
